 About Woodstock MusicWorks \'d0\
\
  Founded in 2007, Woodstock MusicWorks is an independently owned and operated record label based in Woodstock, NY. Our Mission is to harness the vast well of musical talent in the Woodstock area and promote our artists with a non-corporate grassroots approach to the music lovers of the world. Within the Woodstock community lives one of the richest histories in music, and we plan to carry that tradition on for generations by hosting a diverse catalog of artists from a variety of genres and styles that will stand the test of time. For more info visit WoodstockMusicWorks.com\
